{"tid":256218,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視不行了】播唔到星期日足總盃決賽 賠多三個月作為補償","createTime":"2017-05-24T11:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T15:16:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6ce6328980c2cfe62c2c0250f435a6a8e87eb1","tid":256218,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495622218_5c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495622218_5c84.jpg&h=86e1508e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次傳出財困的樂視，一直未有影響到香港業務，但樂視體育今日公佈，因節目調整，本週日(5月28日)凌晨在LeSports HK平台直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)決賽(阿仙奴對車路士)，將無法播出。LeSports HK對本次受影響的用戶鄭重致歉，將提供3個月超級體育組合作為補償。<br />\n<br />\n本報向樂視香港公關查詢無法播放的原因，只獲回覆「因節目調整」，賠償方面亦只得3個月超級體育組合。樂視只表示，如有查詢，可聯繫客戶服務熱線：3956 6666<br />\n<br />\n據了解，與樂視合作播放英超的nowTV並沒有直播的英格蘭足總盃(FA Cup)，如今樂視無法播出，屆時香港可能將沒有合法途徑收看足總盃決賽。<br />\n<br />\n本月初，樂視體育已出現播放問題，包括「韋斯咸：熱刺」英超賽事和一場NBA賽事，令用戶怨聲載道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56737069&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56737069%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=K6hFM7A%2BqeP3hI5k7AlIvKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8f982baf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56737069%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=f9c61f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56737069&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"ce3c75799f4ab817e573c3f71d99013912c8ab86","tid":256218,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"各大聯賽收咧<br />\n可以睇三個月重播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf87e42f5a881609ddc69254cfa4e1ae617ce73","tid":256218,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"屌你馬會定撚左個轉播權再放出黎咪得囉, 有得賭有得播"},{"pid":"6129cc4e31f08213c37f32435191e75beca38827","tid":256218,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}